{"title":"龙年新春早","authors":["黄东成"],"dates":[{"year":2000,"month":2,"day":11}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"龙年新春早"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄东成"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喜庆的锣鼓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刚送走祥和的“兔”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"腾飞的“龙”已跃上舞台，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"定格在春的底版上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一番温热的相互祝福，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"似声声春雷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在人们心上隆隆滚过。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"暖暖的地气开始上升，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冻土层将渐渐溶化，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"处处萌发绿的生命色，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春，漫向天涯。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"龙年新春还有些“冷色”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳却是暖烘烘的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对着太阳做一次深呼吸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吐出胸中郁积的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二氧化碳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冰冻三尺的日子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全部封存进记忆的档案。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"虽还有春寒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"虽还有薄冰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但已不再砭人肌骨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冰碴正溶入潺潺春水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"滋润布谷鸟叫的季节。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"龙年新春，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老人将龙头舞得出神入化，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"舞龙人纷纷脱去棉袄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"光着汗浸浸的胳膊与胸膛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"腾跃在热气腾腾的版图，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凝滞的平静被打破，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"空气里散发着灼烫的气息。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，过不了多久，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"早春的桃花将悄悄抬头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像龙头上簪着的艳红，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一枝，两枝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一点，两点，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尽管色彩还有些浅淡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毕竟大地已渲染亮色。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，春天来了！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}